=head1 DESCRIPTION

An object to define the RoutingCriteria.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Steps => ArrayRef[L<Paws::Connect::RoutingCriteriaInputStep>]

When Amazon Connect does not find an available agent meeting the
requirements in a step for a given step duration, the routing criteria
will move on to the next step sequentially until a join is completed
with an agent. When all steps are exhausted, the contact will be
offered to any agent in the queue.



